### Create Initial Guild Master (ONE TIME ONLY)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/seed

###

### Login
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "guildmaster",
  "password": "changeme123"
}

###

### Get All Users (Replace TOKEN with your JWT token from login)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/users
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Create a Team (Replace TOKEN)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/teams
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alpha Team",
  "description": "Main raid progression team"
}

###

### Create a Team Lead (Replace TOKEN and use actual teamId)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/users
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "teamlead1",
  "password": "secure123",
  "rank": "TEAM_LEAD",
  "teamId": 1
}

###

### Create a Council Member (Replace TOKEN)
POST http://localhost:3001/api/users
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "council1",
  "password": "secure123",
  "rank": "COUNCIL"
}

###

### Get All Teams (Replace TOKEN)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/teams
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Test Health Check (This one works with GET in browser!)
